Enum opencv::core::MatExprResult

source Â· 
pub enum MatExprResult<T> {
    Ok(T),
    Err(Error),
}
Expand description

Intermediate result type thatâ€™s produced by the Mat operations. Call MatExprResult::into_result to get the regular Result.

This type is needed because of Rust orphan rules.
